<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-50 via-white to-blue-50 rounded-3xl shadow-xl" data-controller="exercise-checker">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <!-- Introduction -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-sky-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 mb-3">
      Gli aggettivi qualificativi aggiungono una qualità al nome e possono essere:
    </p>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-sky-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span><strong>grado positivo</strong> → Il libro è interessante.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-sky-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span><strong>comparativo</strong> → più/meno/quanto interessante.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-sky-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span><strong>superlativo</strong> → interessantissimo, molto interessante, il più interessante tra…</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 mt-3 italic">
      Questo libro è interessante. Anzi, è interessantissimo.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 1: Identify adjective degrees -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-blue-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <div class="mb-4 inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-500 to-blue-500 text-white px-3 md:px-6 py-2 rounded-full text-xs md:text-sm font-bold shadow-lg">
      1 IMPARARE TUTTI
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-3">
      Sottolinea gli aggettivi qualificativi nelle frasi e indica il loro grado.
    </h2>

    <% adjective_sentences = [
      { text: "Il tuo cane è più affettuoso del mio.", degree: "comparativo di maggioranza" },
      { text: "Mi piace la chitarra: ha un suono molto dolce.", degree: "superlativo assoluto" },
      { text: "Sara ha i capelli lisci come sua sorella.", degree: "comparativo di uguaglianza" },
      { text: "Per il matrimonio di mia zia ho comprato un abito blu.", degree: "positivo" },
      { text: "Il gelato è meno buono di quello che ho mangiato ieri.", degree: "comparativo di minoranza" },
      { text: "Metti la sciarpa, oggi è una giornata freddissima.", degree: "superlativo assoluto" }
    ] %>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <% adjective_sentences.each_with_index do |sentence, index| %>
        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">- <%= sentence[:text] %></p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-gray-600">(</span>
            <% if index == 0 %>
              <span class="font-semibold text-blue-700"><%= sentence[:degree] %></span>
            <% else %>
              <input type="text"
                     class="flex-1 border-b-2 border-blue-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-700"
                     data-fill-blanks-target="input"
                     data-answer="<%= sentence[:degree] %>"
                     data-correct-answer="<%= sentence[:degree] %>"
                     maxlength="40">
            <% end %>
            <span class="text-gray-600">)</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 2: Superlativo relativo vs assoluto -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-purple-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="word-highlighter" data-word-highlighter-multi-color-value="true">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-purple-700 mb-3 flex items-center flex-wrap gap-2">
      <span class="bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">2</span>
      <span>Clicca sui <span class="text-blue-600">superlativi relativi<span class="inline-block w-6 h-6 bg-blue-300 rounded ml-1 align-middle cursor-pointer transition transform hover:scale-110" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="blue" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span></span> e sui <span class="text-violet-600">superlativi assoluti<span class="inline-block w-6 h-6 bg-violet-300 rounded ml-1 align-middle cursor-pointer transition transform hover:scale-110" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="violet" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span></span>.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-4 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2 cursor-pointer">
      <p>Questo è <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="blue" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">il film più divertente</span> che abbia mai visto.</p>
      <p>Durante la passeggiata nel bosco abbiamo visto degli alberi <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="violet" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">altissimi</span>.</p>
      <p>La torta della nonna è <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="violet" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">buonissima</span>.</p>
      <p>Questo è stato <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="blue" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">il compito più difficile</span> dell'anno.</p>
      <p>Ho comprato un maglione <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="violet" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">caldissimo</span>.</p>
      <p>Oggi è stato <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="blue" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">il giorno meno luminoso</span> della settimana.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 3: Write forms -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-green-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-green-700 mb-3">
      <span class="font-bold">3</span> Scrivi le forme indicate.
    </h2>

    <% forms = [
      { word: "tenero", form: "comparativo di maggioranza", answer: "più tenero" },
      { word: "allegro", form: "comparativo di minoranza", answer: "meno allegro" },
      { word: "alta", form: "comparativo di uguaglianza", answer: "alta come / tanto alta quanto" },
      { word: "saporita", form: "superlativo relativo", answer: "la più saporita" },
      { word: "leggera", form: "superlativo assoluto", answer: "leggerissima / molto leggera" }
    ] %>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <% forms.each do |item| %>
        <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-3 py-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="font-semibold text-green-700"><%= item[:word] %></span>
          <span class="text-gray-600">(<%= item[:form] %>)</span>
          <span class="text-gray-500">→</span>
          <input type="text"
                 class="flex-1 min-w-[200px] border-b-2 border-green-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-green-700"
                 data-fill-blanks-target="input"
                 data-answer="<%= item[:answer] %>"
                 data-correct-answer="<%= item[:answer] %>"
                 maxlength="40">
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 4: Complete with adjectives -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-orange-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-orange-700 mb-3">
      <span class="font-bold">4</span> Completa con aggettivi al grado richiesto.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-orange-50 border-2 border-orange-200 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">Cristian è</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-orange-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-orange-700 min-w-[150px]" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="il più alto">
          <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">(superlativo relativo)</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">tra i compagni di basket.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-orange-50 border-2 border-orange-200 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">Ho comprato un</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-orange-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-orange-700 min-w-[150px]" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="bellissimo">
          <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">(superlativo assoluto)</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">libro di poesie.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-orange-50 border-2 border-orange-200 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">Le scarpe da ginnastica di Alice sono</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-orange-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-orange-700 min-w-[150px]" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="rosse">
          <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">(positivo)</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-orange-50 border-2 border-orange-200 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">La campanella della scuola è</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-orange-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-orange-700 min-w-[150px]" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="rumorosissima">
          <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">(superlativo assoluto)</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-orange-50 border-2 border-orange-200 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">Simonetta è</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-orange-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-orange-700 min-w-[150px]" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="più alta">
          <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">(comparativo di maggioranza)</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">di Paolo.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-orange-50 border-2 border-orange-200 rounded-xl px-3 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">Il Po è</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-orange-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 focus:outline-none focus:border-orange-700 min-w-[150px]" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="il più lungo">
          <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">(superlativo relativo)</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">dei fiumi d'Italia.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-right text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">
    Esercizi pp. <%= link_to "154", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p154"), class: "text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-800 underline" %>, <%= link_to "155", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p155"), class: "text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-800 underline" %> e <%= link_to "163", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p163"), class: "text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-800 underline" %>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise Controls -->
  <div class="mt-6">
    <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls', color: 'sky', current_page: 'nvl5_gram_p052' %>
  </div>
</div>
